tool_description: Provide all OSM data inside a building
title: osm-indoor-building

api_list.name: Building indoor data in json
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://osm-indoor-building.p.rapidapi.com/osm/places/way/{id}/related/json"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "osm-indoor-building.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
